{"tid":2145610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應個人資料被美方公開　曾國衞︰與私隱專員公署商討","createTime":"2020-08-08T06:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T06:56:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05505965549b6123e67020f8456085a37985186f","tid":2145610,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:41:19.000Z","msg":"美國宣布制裁11名香港與內地官員及前官員，並在網上列出有關人士的資料。在名單上的政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞接受本台訪問時批評，美國作為所謂民主自由和尊重人權的國家，卻肆意「起底」和公開個人資料，是要被譴責的行為，亦是流氓的行徑。<br />\n<br />\n至於可以如何跟進，曾國衞說會與個人資料私隱專員公署商討，以及與律政司研究，考慮需要採取的適當行動。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞表示，他在美國沒有任何資產，亦不會前往美國，有關制裁完全不會影響他，他所做的事完全是為國家和為香港，理直氣壯，完全不用擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542562-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542562-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=c8f84398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542562-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=23f28d0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542562-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6bcefecb945b7a8ad3451cc1e28e2dbb29166048","tid":2145610,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"人頭豬,你真係蠢,唔係扮喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7913a6f7ce95399c4aa117ceccb0e8c7482b199","tid":2145610,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"4fd5578d526cb8c9cff25a3ea4d9a93bfeacd3b0","tid":2145610,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"佢嘅商討係想限制香港人自己share 呢d資料，有人share又確認到身份嘅就捉佢地，而唔係向美國出手"},{"pid":"f584cbcd9480d341fba69a96b80df6c930ac84d2","tid":2145610,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202